---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Navbar } from "../components/Navbar";
import { Article } from '../components/Article.jsx';
import {Footer} from '../components/Footer';
import {ScrollUpButton} from '../components/ScrollUpButton';

const pageData = {
    title: "Private and policy",
    subtitle: "",
    date: "June 5, 2024",
    content: `
    <h3>1. Introduction</h3>

Welcome to our website. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our web development and marketing services.

<h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>

We collect the following types of information:

- Email addresses and correspondence when you contact us via email
- Usage data through Google Analytics
- Website performance data through Google Search Console

<h3>3. How We Use Your Information</h3>

We use the collected information for:

- Responding to your inquiries and providing customer service
- Marketing purposes, including sending information about our services
- Analyzing website traffic and improving our services
- Understanding how visitors interact with our website

<h3>4. Google Analytics and Search Console</h3>

We use Google Analytics and Google Search Console to collect data about website usage. This includes:

- Website traffic statistics
- User behavior on our website
- Search performance data

You can learn more about Google's privacy practices at [Google's Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy).

<h3>5. Data Storage and Protection</h3>

We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information. Your email correspondence is stored securely and accessed only by authorized personnel.

<h3>6. Marketing Communications</h3>

If you contact us via email, we may use your email address for marketing purposes. You can opt out of marketing communications at any time by contacting us.

<h3>7. Your Rights</h3>

You have the right to:

- Request access to your personal data
- Request correction of your personal data
- Request deletion of your personal data
- Object to processing of your personal data

<h3>8. Contact Information</h3>

For any privacy-related questions or concerns, please contact us via email.

<h3>9. Changes to This Policy</h3>

We reserve the right to update this privacy policy at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the website.`
}

---
<Layout title="Website Design | SEO Services | Website Maintenance">
    <Navbar client:load />
    <Article articleData={pageData} />
    <Footer />
    <ScrollUpButton client:load />
</Layout>

<style is:global>
    h3{
        @apply text-secondaryColor text-sm sm:text-base  mb-6 mt-16  font-bold;
    }
</style>